OL,3,CUnited Utilities to increase water
OL,4,Cbills by 32%
OL,6,FWater company United Utilities has
OL,7,Fconfirmed it will raise water bills
OL,8,Ffor its customers by 32% over the next
OL,9,Ffive years, while increasing dividend
OL,10,Fpayouts to shareholders.
OL,12,FUnited Utilities, which provides water
OL,13,Fto around seven million people across
OL,14,FGreater Manchester and Liverpool, said
OL,15,Fthey had agreed the bill increases
OL,16,Fwhich were negotiated with the
OL,17,Fregulator Ofwat in 2024.
