OL,3,CUnited Utilities to increase water
OL,4,Cbills by 32%
OL,6,FThe decision which was made by the
OL,7,Fregulator in December, means the
OL,8,Ftypical bill payer across the UK will
OL,9,Fsee their payments rise by an average
OL,10,Fof #86 this April.
OL,12,FThe increases come amid high levels of
OL,13,Fsewage spills and underinvestment in
OL,14,Fpipes, sewers and reservoirs over the
OL,15,Flast 10 years.
OL,17,FUnited Utilities have said it needs to
OL,18,Fincrease bills to pay for improvements
OL,19,Fto their infrastructure to reduce
OL,20,Fpollution incidents.
