OL,3,CUnited Utilities to increase water
OL,4,Cbills by 32%
OL,6,FDespite this, the company said they
OL,7,Fwill raise dividend payouts to
OL,8,Fshareholders this year so that they
OL,9,Fincrease in line with inflation.
OL,11,FCEO of United Utilities, Louise
OL,12,FBeardmore, said the rise in bills
OL,13,Fwould raise #13 billion to invest in
OL,14,Fits infrastructure across the North
OL,15,FWest.
OL,17,FShe said the total was the "largest
OL,18,Finvestment in water and wastewater
OL,19,Finfrastructure in over 100 years".
